snippet.title: Johnny Depp loses defamation case against The Sun over Amber Heard 'wife-beater' article | ABC News
snippet.description:
Actor Johnny Depp has lost a high-stakes battle against a newspaper that called him a 'wife beater'. A UK court has found that most of the allegatins made against Depp were true. The ruling deals a big blow to the actor's reputation and career. Nick Dole reports from London.
